{"tid":1866793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【開放討論】醫護會唔會考慮釋出善意？","createTime":"2020-02-07T01:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T02:03:27.000Z","uid":340160,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f3821333b3d202ecbf466a89a49996e28b5b401c","tid":1866793,"uid":340160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:45:05.000Z","msg":"剩低一大要求（唔係訴求）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全面封關</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n名義上釋出善意<br />\n<br />\n實質統一輿論戰<br />\n應對港共<strong>冷處理</strong>招數<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[1]</span><br />\n<br />\n以免港共<strong>部分妥協</strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">[2]</span><br />\nspin走全面封關<br />\n<br />\n可以再度要求<span style=\"color: red;\">同林鄭公開對話</span><br />\n否則無限期罷工<br />\n<br />\n扭轉頹勢<br />\n招攬更多醫護參與<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">終極罷工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n緊記 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一鼓作氣 再而衰 三而竭</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n諗唔諗得過？<br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">好文分享<br />\n<br />\n「長文」唔係一個醫護，但處理過其他國家嘅罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1860673/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1860673/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n[1] To 醫護及香港人：對方一定拖得就拖，從而試探底線，拖到有人出事下推比你地。你地會好大壓力，但同樣佢地都係。<br />\n<br />\n[2] To 所有醫護：部分妥協會比全部破裂後果更慘<br />\n可參考商業下，成功爭取加人工後一定會狂加工時及減福利，你會比冇加人工更慘。要贏一定要全部都贏，一定要保障冇秋後算賬，齊上齊落</span>"},{"pid":"e3ed9ccf8c9c7e67ce374ca8d6f5a3576ddb82b8","tid":1866793,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"522241f113ffef8cacfd534e4383819d1fd889e4","tid":1866793,"uid":340160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"求幫推"},{"pid":"94c6321de95ba1a6f2c7ad1c847a0c21af0ff94c","tid":1866793,"uid":340160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWmh2Yf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWmh2Yf.jpg&h=7909a022&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12b5963d04ef343c46ac6d7b8201c0e475653b38","tid":1866793,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點會得一個訴求？防疫除咗阻擋疫區病人入侵，仲要清除香港內既隱形病人<br />\n驅逐支那病人刻不容緩，酒店賓館要交出名單，全部要遣返"},{"pid":"72c88c158163b69774f67143ef5a78ea0b690e24","tid":1866793,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n醫護唔夠ppe 救人等於送頭"},{"pid":"76752978674bfb729285bcd264a3a248a8c25ffd","tid":1866793,"uid":340160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72c88c158163b69774f67143ef5a78ea0b690e24","tid":1866793,"uid":272603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:49:02.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n醫護唔夠ppe 救人等於送頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:55:58.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工由始至終都係要求港共封關<br />\n<br />\n封唔到關 有口罩都死<br />\n<br />\n咁不如直接從單一方向擊破港共"},{"pid":"e04cbb3f3956c737e11ec17853140fd77aadc6f0","tid":1866793,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"政府既奸計係唔會得逞既！！！"}],"pinned":{"pid":"94c6321de95ba1a6f2c7ad1c847a0c21af0ff94c","tid":1866793,"uid":340160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWmh2Yf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWmh2Yf.jpg&h=7909a022&s={SIZE}\" />"}}